prompts.frontCover: Greeting card front cover, beautiful flat 2D botanical illustration. A humorous and charming beach scene. Cartoon illustrated versions of Lao Lao and Jordan from the reference photo are building a giant, elaborate sandcastle together on a sunny beach. Jordan, wearing his tan hoodie, is comically struggling to place a tiny flag on the very top of the wobbly sandcastle tower. Lao Lao, in her light blue sweatshirt, is laughing joyfully as she holds a bucket and shovel, patting the base of the sandcastle to keep it steady. The scene is framed by a beautiful, lush botanical border of tropical leaves like monstera and palm fronds, with hibiscus flowers woven in. The overall vibe is playful, bright, and loving. In the center, below the couple, the text "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao" is written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script. Soft, warm color palette. Clean white background.
